question: Subway World Series?
description:
This Market refers to the 2024 MLB Playoffs.

If the New York Yankees defeat the Cleveland Guardians in the American League Championship Series AND the New York Mets defeat the Los Angeles Dodgers in the National League Championship Series, this market will resolve to "Yes". Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

If it becomes impossible for both of these teams to advance to the World Series (i.e. either team loses their respective league championship series), this market will resolve to "No".

The resolution source will be MLB.com.
